title: MNF Recap & The Season Doesn't Start Until After Thanksgiving (Boy, oh, boy, big news)
itunes:title: MNF Recap & The Season Doesn't Start Until After Thanksgiving (Boy, oh, boy, big news)
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap the Ravens stomping on the Rams. After MNF, Chris Wesseling shows the guys a surprise video (21:15)and then the heroes give predictions for the rest of the season.(29:20)They close the show by previewing the Thanksgiving day games. (51:05)
